              any policy changes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="p-8 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
          >
            <h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-3">
              What factors affect my BC PNP scoring the most?
            </h3>
