          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Strategic Tips -->
      <div
        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600 to-red-800 p-10 rounded-[3rem] text-white"
      >
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">
          Strategic Tips
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            <strong>Maximize Your Wage:</strong> Negotiate the highest possible hourly
            wage with your BC employer, as this category offers the most points (55
            max).
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Consider Regional Jobs:</strong> Job offers outside Metro Vancouver
            can add up to 25 bonus points, potentially making the difference between
            receiving an ITA or not.
